346
00:16:21,640 --> 00:16:22,719
There must be a way.

347
00:16:23,559 --> 00:16:24,280
The Storehouse!

348
00:16:24,425 --> 00:16:25,599
Isn’t there a piece of

349
00:16:25,599 --> 00:16:26,880
Dragon Horn in the Storehouse?

350
00:16:26,880 --> 00:16:27,840
