354
00:16:33,875 --> 00:16:34,719
Go now!

355
00:16:34,719 --> 00:16:35,679
Your Majesty...

356
00:16:36,425 --> 00:16:37,119
Yes, Your Majesty.

357
00:16:37,359 --> 00:16:38,039
Yes, Your Majesty.

