378
00:18:07,125 --> 00:18:08,025
Then this is...

379
00:18:09,439 --> 00:18:12,359
Dragon Horn is an elixir
to extend one’s life.

380
00:18:13,520 --> 00:18:15,119
Lord Qinghai should be fine

381
00:18:15,119 --> 00:18:16,199
