384
00:18:20,725 --> 00:18:21,900
I’m afraid

385
00:18:22,000 --> 00:18:23,479
we need to find

386
00:18:23,880 --> 00:18:25,000
something rarer than Dragon Horn

387
00:18:25,000 --> 00:18:26,599
to save Lord Qinghai.

