00:20:11,640 --> 00:20:13,079
Fang Zhiyi pretended to surrender.

425
00:20:14,239 --> 00:20:16,839
On July 2nd in the 27th year of Lintai,

426
00:20:17,160 --> 00:20:18,400
Emperor Xiu had a serious fever

