00:20:22,680 --> 00:20:23,920
The late emperor died

430
00:20:23,920 --> 00:20:25,959
before the last Lord Qinghai.

431
00:20:26,760 --> 00:20:28,239
But the book doesn’t say

432
00:20:28,239 --> 00:20:30,825
