00:23:49,079 --> 00:23:50,050
Go back.

504
00:23:51,800 --> 00:23:52,520
Your Highness!

505
00:23:52,520 --> 00:23:53,079
Your Highness.

506
00:23:53,079 --> 00:23:53,920
- Your Highness!
- Your Highness.

507
00:23:54,400 --> 00:23:55,599
I’m begging you.

508
00:23:56,199 --> 00:23:57,079
Please

509
00:23:57,079 --> 00:23:58,920
