511
00:24:03,475 --> 00:24:04,675
Get up first.

512
00:24:06,850 --> 00:24:07,680
Thank you, Your Highness.

513
00:24:07,680 --> 00:24:09,319
What happened?

514
00:24:09,800 --> 00:24:10,560
Tell me.

515
00:24:10,560 --> 00:24:12,675
